-Yep.
-Yep.

26:12.279 --> 26:14.822
-Okay, it's looking good.
-We're free here.

26:14.907 --> 26:16.950
-We're free here.
-Oh, God.

26:17.034 --> 26:18.534
What am l down to?

26:18.619 --> 26:20.787
Hey, we're loose in the front finally!

26:20.871 --> 26:22.413
-All right.
-Yeah !

26:22.498 --> 26:24.874
(CHEERlNG AND APPLAUSE)

