WENTZ: That moment,
when we made that separation,

26:32.049 --> 26:36.678
that was probably
the highest point of my life.

26:37.513 --> 26:39.305
-How was that?
-Champagne.

26:39.390 --> 26:40.932
-Hide it.
-(LAUGHS)

26:41.016 --> 26:42.725
-Hide it. (LAUGHS)
-(LAUGHTER)

