26:45.771 --> 26:46.813
This whole. . . l don't know.

26:47.398 --> 26:48.856
-Cheers.
-Just, "Cheers."

26:48.983 --> 26:50.692
-You ready?
-Ready.

26:50.776 --> 26:52.402
-To Sue.
-To old Sue.

26:52.486 --> 26:53.820
-Sue.
-Sue.

26:54.863 --> 26:56.489
Yeah.

26:57.324 --> 26:58.866
-(LAUGHS)
-Yeah.

