We had a buzzer on our door,

27:43.245 --> 27:46.331
so that if anybody came in,
it would buzz back in the prep lab

27:46.415 --> 27:48.499
and we could go meet them
in the front office.

27:48.625 --> 27:52.086
lt was about 7:00 in the morning
when the buzzer went off.

