01:26:49.872 --> 01:26:51.581
that the only way to get her
away from Maurice Williams

01:26:51.665 --> 01:26:53.374
was through Sotheby's.

01:26:53.458 --> 01:26:56.878
All of us were aware that
the auction was taking place.

