lt would probably sell for $1 or $2 million.

01:26:59.590 --> 01:27:03.843
The big fear was that it was going to be
sold to some private individual.

01:27:03.927 --> 01:27:08.598
l know there were a lot of people
concerned that it might be bought

01:27:08.682 --> 01:27:10.224
by an institution in a foreign country.

