was that it was gonna be sold
and lost to science

01:27:14.479 --> 01:27:17.481
and sold and
put in a private room someplace.

01:27:17.649 --> 01:27:22.320
We always felt an extraordinary obligation
to get this fossil to the right home.

01:27:22.404 --> 01:27:26.157
Clearly there were a lot
of really interested parties

01:27:26.241 --> 01:27:28.743
